data.description: Elegant and spacious, this modern masterpiece boasts four bedrooms and three bathrooms, including two luxurious master suites. Situated on a .45 acre lot, this home has been fully updated with meticulous attention to detail. As you approach the property, you are greeted by a charming privacy fence that encloses the corner lot. Step inside to discover an inviting enclosed patio, perfect for relaxing or entertaining guests. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living areas, creating a harmonious flow throughout the home. With its abundance of natural light and contemporary design elements, this property exudes sophistication and style. Additionally, there is a convenient shop on the premises that offers endless possibilities for hobbies or storage needs. Don't miss your chance to own this exceptional residence that combines modern elegance with timeless charm.
